LAST FIRST DAY 📝
•
I created this visual to embody the emotions of how a lot of college students feel about school, especially with me being in the last semester of my senior year! Don’t get me wrong I’m bout my degree! But, every now and then you can get heated about school along with being excited about what you’ve accomplished so this is a visual interpretation of that. 
 •
I was inspired by @jasiahpowers & @moniqueyvonn work which made me step outside of my comfort zone and do something I’ve wanted to do for a while and creatively director and edit visuals.
•
Thank you @ohmyjoyy for helping me bring my concept to life and being such an amazing friend and artist! FLICKS OTW!

Song: Boys Wanna Be Her- Peaches

Came here for school, graduated to the high life❕

I stand here before you as a  graduate of thee Morgan State University with my Bachelor of Science degree in Strategic Communication! I wouldn’t be here without my parents, sister, family, and friends who have encouraged and pushed me to my highest potential to achieve such an amazing accomplishment. I’m happy to say that I stuck with something and reached the light at the end. I’m so excited to see what opportunities the world has for me and to continue learning about life and find myself and my purpose in this new chapter.
BIG GRADUATE! What? Like it’s Hard?! 

Love,
Jabari2.0 Thompson
